My personal highlight of this year was releasing the “Infatuation” video which required @thedoloshow and I to trek and battle through the desert to film. 😅😤(story will be in my book 10+ years from now)
BUT THE REAL HIGHLIGHT IS ALL YOU WHO CONTINUE TO LISTEN AND SUPPORT MY MUSIC. 🙏🏽🙏🏽❤️❤️ 
As an artist the journey is not easy but little reminders like #spotifywrapped helps me to put things into perspective. 
Thank you I LOVE YOU. 
And damn I cant wait for you to hear/see my new shit!!! #2023 🔥🔥🔥
